        <div class="content-body">
          <p>Every successful study abroad journey begins with a conversation. Grant Consulting offers a completely free initial consultation where our experienced advisors sit down with you to understand your academic background, career ambitions, and personal circumstances. There is no obligation and no pressure — just an honest, informative session designed to help you understand your options.</p>
          <p>During your consultation, we conduct a thorough profile assessment that evaluates your grades, test scores, language proficiency, extracurricular activities, and financial situation. This gives us a clear picture of where you stand and allows us to provide realistic, tailored advice rather than generic recommendations. We believe every student deserves to know exactly what is achievable before making any commitments.</p>
          <p>By the end of your free session, you will walk away with a personalized path recommendation outlining the countries, universities, and programs that best match your profile and goals. We also discuss potential scholarship opportunities, estimated timelines, and the next steps you would need to take. Whether you choose to continue working with us or pursue your applications independently, the consultation gives you the clarity to move forward with confidence.</p>
        </div>

